                    "text": "Web Development"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Java is a popular choice for building dynamic web applications, often using frameworks like JavaServer Faces (JSF), Spring MVC, and JavaServer Pages (JSP)."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
